arts.ttl: Luis Suárez leads Inter Miami to 3-1 win over Pumas in Leagues Cup
arts.sum: De Paul, the star Argentine midfielder who came to MLS to play with his national team friend Messi, made his club debut in Inter Miami’s League’s Cup opener against Atlas last Wednesday and had two assists against Necaxa. Luis Suárez scored and had two assists, and Inter Miami beat Pumas 3-1 on Wednesday night to advance in the Leagues Cup.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami 3–1 Pumas UNAM: Player Ratings As Luis Suarez Sends Herons to Leagues Cup Knockout Stage
arts.sum: The Herons put in their best performance of the tournament so far despite missing the injured Lionel Messi.

arts.ttl: Why Lionel Messi Isn’t Playing for Inter Miami vs. Pumas UNAM
arts.sum: Lionel Messi will only be able to watch as Inter Miami look to punch their tickets to the Leagues Cup knockout stage.

arts.ttl: Inter Miami Receive Huge Selection Boost Ahead of Leagues Cup Phase One Finale vs. Pumas
arts.sum: Maximiliano Falcón will be available for the Herons’ final Phase One game after a red card was rescinded.
